Glow Fun Run/Walk registrations are due today by 3:30 if you want your t shirt the day of the event. We will accept registrations the day of the event and we will order your t shirt then. This event will be held on the FIT trail and starts at the Shores and continues to the railroad tracks and back.
Our NHS volleyball tournament has room in the 7th and 8th grade divisions. Registration is $80 for teams and we should be done by noon or shortly after on October 19.
These events help to sponsor our service activities throughout the community and more and to help fund the academic awards banquet in March.
Please contact me (jschany@e-hawks.org) or Kelly Josephson (kjosephson@e-hawks.org) if you have questions.
Registration forms for everything are included below!
